		<!-- message -->
		<div>First, a bit of description of my history with EQ.. I've been playing approximately 5 months.. have a wizard 65 (sage) just over 90 AA's.  Joined a &quot;family guild&quot; which was pleasant, but wasn't progressing.. I desire to be more productive within groups.. and even more so I desire to see the elemental planes.. and well the zones the game has to offer.  In response to that growing desire I joined a guild with a stronger raiding focus and since have gotten vt keyed and am  currently thumping away in that zone with my guild and inbetween vt sessions were working on planar progression.  I do not multi-box characters.. for me, just would reduce the fun of it..  Now that I've given you an idea of my background, I have a few questions that may seem naive, but are truly earnest ...<br />
<br />
1)  CoH and mages.. just don't understand why they have this ability.. they can summon, have pets.. and nuke very strongly.. if any class should of gotten this, it's the wizard in my opinion..   Can anyone explain this to me.<br />
<br />
2)  I hear much about &quot;interdependence of classes&quot; ... I know multi boxing is prevalent on my server... I've seen ppl 4-box regularly.  Does anyone else think this &quot;interdependence&quot; is nothing more than a money-making tool for SOE.  Can't we have both soloing aspects and groups?  especially since Sony does say the wizard is a good fit for both.. *chuckles*<br />
<br />
3)  Rain/Pillars/al'kabor line of spells.. is there a person that doesn't think these need refinement in the least?<br />
<br />
4)  Is there a class any less desirable for a grp than a wizard?  Particularly in GoD... ??<br />
<br />
5)  Why don't we have at least one defense against summoning?  Something that can empower this class... why?<br />
<br />
6) shackles.. why do  ppl ask for an increased time on shackles... are we masters of Dps bursts beyond rival?.. *cough* .. Doesn't the fact so many request this proves there is a problem?<br />
<br />
7)  LFG wizards.. common on ur server?  Ever done a who all wizard when a raid isn't occurring?  Am I the only one to notice just how few people actually play this class?  Doesn't this lack of interest in the class indicate the HUGE problems the class is currently suffering?<br />
<br />
Ok.. nuff of that.. positives..<br />
<br />
1)  what's max crit on a manaburn and is it really worth the aa pts<br />
<br />
2)  whats the single most important AA for a wizard...<br />
<br />
3)  Does anyone get a charge when u crit an watch the mobs health bar plummet lol<br />
<br />
just some stuff off the top of my head... forgive me if much has been addressed in previous threads.. but these forums are very active.. <br />
<br />
OHH<br />
<br />
Ward of Destruction... can anyone tell me if this is worthwhile.. any range / dmg stats..... seems to me this could possibly be worthwhile if they did it right.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
